slides.onboarding.welcome.description.string: It’s a space to co-create stunning presentations that bring your audience into the conversation. Figma Slides is free in beta, through early 2025. After that, new pricing may apply. {learn_more}

slides.onboarding.new_slide.description.string: Choose from dozens of templates— from full decks to simple styles—and quickly add a new slide with ⇧S.

slides.onboarding.views.description.string: Hit Shift + Period (⇧.) to switch views. Use grid view to outline and organize, or slide view to dive into the details.

slides.onboarding.nondesigner.tools.titl.string: Pick the right tool for the job

slides.onboarding.nondesigner.tools.desc.string: Along with simple slide tools, you can run a poll, embed a prototype, and add assets for some extra oomph.

slides.onboarding.designer.tools.descrip.string: Use slides mode to get started, then switch to design mode to perfect and polish your deck.

slides.onboarding.share.description.string: When you’re ready, you can present your deck in one tab while reading your notes in another.
